data.description: INVESTOR ALERT! This immaculate and well-maintained quiet home is perfect to live and produce income with MIL as vacation rental. The home features most everything you want! Remodeled Galley and bathrooms. New Hardwood Laminate, Porcelain Tile, and high-end stain proof carpet. Keep you bills low with 6 mini-split heat pumps and propane free standing stove! Newer 2-bedroom MIL is fully furnished w/separate entrance and fenced side yard! Home features cement plank siding, newer roof w/high end features, Milgard windows. Plenty of parking w/separate 1 car garage and attached 2 car garage w/220 and utility sink! Large Green House, gardens, and firepit! Easy access to sounder train and Hwy 512.  This is a must see home!
